		<div class="content-step-text">
			<h3>
				Pricing
			</h3>
			    <p>
				    Valuation is a key part of the selling process, it is vital to have an accurate value
                    for your property. In order to do this, make use of the various
                    <a href="http://www.zoopla.co.uk/home-values/">housing price estimators</a>
                    on sites we list to such as Zoopla and doing research on
                    <a href="http://www.zoopla.co.uk/house-prices/?search_source=top_nav">recent sales</a>
                    in the area and try to identify trends.
			    </p>
			    <p>
				    Many traditional estate agents offer valuations for free, so it is vital that you get
                    multiple estimates on your house, as well as tracking the sale price of houses in your area.
			    </p>
		</div>

		<hr class="divider-bar"></hr>	

		<div class="content-image">
			<img class="stepImage" src="media.jpg">
		</div>

		<div class="content-step-text">
			<h3>
				Media
			</h3>
			    <p>
			        While listing a property with us, you will be prompted to upload media about your
                    property. This is a vital part of marketing that will help you sell your property.
                    Making sure all photos that are uploaded are of a good quality goes a long way to
                    enticing potential buyers.
			    </p>
			    <p>
			        It is important not to mislead the buyer, but to provide informative descriptions of
                    key features of the property, and good images that showcase the selling points.
			    </p>
                <p>
                    For advice on how to take the best pictures for each room
                    <a href="advice.html">
                        click here.
                    </a>
                </p>
			
		</div>

